rComments: She's nice, but you have to do most of your advising on your own, and always double-check her work.

Shes an advisor: I hate her. Useless in advising, you need to prod her to do anything helpful for you, dismissive, cant answer your questions properly or correctly half the time; I dont think she knows any of the (old or new) requirements imposed on Spanish majors. I dont think she cares for her job either; I wish she would leave immediately.
